headline: AM Best Affirms Credit Ratings of Triple Crown Assurance Co.
summary: OLDWICK, N.J., September 18, 2025--AM Best has affirmed the Financial Strength Rating of A- (Excellent) and the Long-Term Issuer Credit Rating of "a-" (Excellent) of Triple Crown Assurance Co. (TCA) (Dallas, TX). The outlook of these Credit Ratings (ratings) is stable.
